{"tid":1924184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"監狗會下周公開會議只作網上直播 不設公眾和傳媒席","createTime":"2020-03-13T14:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T14:23:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce805f4237fc9f8fb0622c25a43f78bc60b4eb91","tid":1924184,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"監警會下周公開會議只作網上直播 記協不滿不設答問<br />\n<br />\n監警會下星期二，將與投訴警察課代表舉行例會。根據公開會議部分的議程，將會報告投訴警察課的每月統計數字、刑事及違反紀律事項，和因反修例引發的大型公眾活動相關投訴數字，亦會由警方簡報「大型公眾活動中暴力升級的情況」。監警會表示，因應防疫和保障在場人士健康，公開會議部分，會透過網上直播對外公開，會場內不設公眾和傳媒席。<br />\n<br />\n記協得悉會議不設傳媒提問環節，對此不滿，指有關安排令會議透明度大減，亦令傳媒無法一如以往與主席及委員溝通，由於有關議題受公眾高度關注，已去信要求監警會，在會議後安排傳媒採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273513&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1273513%26csid%3D261_341&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=4a2775ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273513&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"c96aef9d443cd47ea3489fdcefabd5e898ebe92a","tid":1924184,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"反對23條立法聯盟簽署<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ/formResponse\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ%2FformResponse&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=f2c99d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ/formResponse</a>"}]}